# zero-arena-bacend hosts three services that DO NOT share configuration:
#
#   • dataset service   →  copy `.env.dataset.example` into `.env`
#   • oracle  service   →  copy `.env.oracle.example`  into `.env`
#   • paper   service   →  copy `.env.paper.example`   into `.env`
#
# In production they should run on different hosts. They never need to
# share keys — operator-gas, oracle-signer, and paper-updater are three
# distinct roles with different threat models.
#
# Either way: this file is a stub. Do not paste secrets here.
